title: UP-The Dempsey Sisters [2013]
description:
UP-The Dempsey Sisters (2013) 

Air Date: 28 Dec 2013

Summary: Deena, Sheena, and Tina Dempsey are sisters who have always shared everything growing up, including 

their love for singing! Fast forward to over a decade since their last performance, and the girls find themselves 

going through the motions, working average 9 to 5 jobs just to get by and make ends meet. The loss of her very 

posh and stable job ends up being the catalyst that catapults Deena into a place she never thought she'd find 

herself again; chasing her dream to sing. With the help of her older brother Thad who shows up on her doorstep 

with a parallel dream and a brand new wife, Deena plots to convince Sheena and Tina that it's not over until the 

Dempsey Sisters sing!
